quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,40,"Àti pé ní òru àti ni ẹ̀yìn ìrun ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ fún Un."
  50,41,"Kí o sì tẹ́tí sí (ọ̀rọ̀) ọjọ́ tí olùpèpè yóò pèpè láti àyè kan tó súnmọ́."
  50,42,"Ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò gbọ́ igbe pẹ̀lú òdodo. Ìyẹn ni ọjọ́ ìjáde ẹ̀dá (láti inú sàréè)."
  51,34,"Wọ́n ti fi àmì sí i lára lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ fún àwọn alákọyọ.”"
  51,35,"Nítorí náà, A mú àwọn tó jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo jáde kúrò nínú (ìlú náà)."
  51,36,"A kò sì rí nínú (ìlú náà) yàtọ̀ sí ilé kan tó jẹ́ ti àwọn mùsùlùmí."
  52,25,"Apá kan wọn yóò dojú kọ apá kan, wọn yó sì máa bèèrè ọ̀rọ̀ lọ́wọ́ ara wọn."
  52,26,"Wọn yóò sọ pé: “Dájúdájú tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ àwa máa ń páyà láààrin àwọn ènìyàn wa."
  52,27,"Ṣùgbọ́n Allāhu ṣàánú wa. Ó sì là wá kúrò níbi ìyà Iná."
  53,19,"Ẹ sọ fún mi nípa òrìṣà Lāt àti òrìṣà ‘Uzzā,"
  53,20,"àti Mọnāh, òrìṣà kẹta mìíràn.1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Hajj;  22:52.]
  53,21,"Ṣé ọmọkùnrin ni tiyín, ọmọbìnrin sì ni tiRẹ̀?"
  54,10,"Nítorí náà, ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú wọ́n ti borí mi. Bá mi gbẹ̀san.”"
  54,11,"Nítorí náà, A ṣí àwọn ìlẹ̀kùn sánmọ̀ sílẹ̀ pẹ̀lú omi tó lágbára."
  54,12,"A tún mú àwọn odò ṣàn jáde láti inú ilẹ̀. Omi (sánmọ̀) pàdé (omi ilẹ̀) pẹ̀lú àṣẹ tí A ti kọ (lé wọn lórí)."
  55,4,"Ó sì fi àlàyé (ọ̀rọ̀ sísọ) mọ̀ ọ́n."
  55,5,"Òòrùn àti òṣùpá (ń rìn) fún ìṣírò (ọjọ́ ayé)."
  55,6,"Àwọn ìtàkùn ilẹ̀ àti igi ń forí kanlẹ̀ (fún Allāhu)."